body: Y’all, we only have 38 days left until Captain Marvel comes out, 88 days until Avengers: Endgame, and 158 days until Spider-Man: Far From Home. But like. Focus on Captain Marvel for now… 38 days!!! and then just 50 days after that until Endgame! and then just 70 days until Far From home! BUT THIRTY EIGHT DAYS UNTIL CAPTAIN MARVEL Y’ALL WE’RE GONNA MAKE IT, WE’RE GONNA LIVE!

blog.description:
Super-hero-confessions is a blog where you can submit your confessions/personal opinions about any of the super hero movies, comics, television shows, cartoons, etc.

The confessions that are posted are those that are submitted; not the opinions of the blog owners. All the confessions will be anonymous when posted. Feel free to submit photos along with your confession if you would like as well.

If you want us to see a post tag it with either #superheroconfessions or #superhero confessions

title: 10 New High-Res Captain Marvel Stills
body:
10 New High-Res #CaptainMarvel Stills

Following some magazine exclusives for Captain Marvel, Disney has made the new images that debuted in those magazines available in high-resolution and not stamped.

Most of these images are from the recent issue of Empire magazine, and there are a couple high-res stills in here from the latest special look TV spot. There’s also a high-res look at both Ronin and Carol on Earth in the red & blue…
